desc: Elsa Libero - Specialising in vintage and antique jewellery with beautiful pieces from the Victorian, Georgian and Edwardian eras including Art Deco and Art Nouveau pieces through to the 1980s. Our collection includes rings, brooches, pendants, bracelets, necklaces and various other items of interest.

layout.text:
"I've never thought of my jewelery as trophies. I'm here to take care of it and to love it, for we are only temporary custodians of beauty."
Elizabeth Taylor
